<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="card">
      <img class="card-img-top" src="starship.jpg" alt="Starship">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h4 class="card-title">Starship</h4>
          <p class="card-text">Once upon a time, in a far away galaxy. There was a young team on the Discovery Starship</p>
          <div class="btn btn-primary"><%= link_to 'Take me to the story', story_path(1), class: 'css_style', style: 'color:white' %></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <img class="card-img-top" src="wonderland.jpg" alt="wonderland">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h4 class="card-title">Wonderland</h4>
        <p class="card-text">Wondering down a forest path, Alex feels drawn to the mysterious flowers that seem to form a wall along the path. Suddenly the road forks, where should she go? To the left or to the right?</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Take me to there</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <img class="card-img-top" src="far_far_away.jpg" alt="Far_away">
      <div class="card-body">
        <h4 class="card-title">Far far away</h4>
        <p class="card-text">Since Sam told James about the magical kingdom of Far Far Away. James hasn't been able to think about anything else, should he go? Would you go?</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Take me to there</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
